Two non-players also have honorary jerseys hanging in the rafters:
* 1 [[阿維達斯·薩博尼斯|阿維達斯·薩博尼斯]], 中鋒, 1995-03, as #1 is still used by team players (currently guard [[Jarrett_Jack|Jarrett Jack]]).
* 2 [[拉里·韦恩伯格|拉里·韦恩伯格]], Team founder-owner, 1970-88.  Jersey is honorary, as #2 is still used by team players (currently guard [[Steve_Blake|Steve Blake]]).
* 77 [[杰克·拉姆齐|杰克·拉姆齐]], 主教練, 1976-86.  Number selected in honor of 1976-77 season.

